ist of Essential Medicines a list of the most important medication needed in a basic health system Flukonazole Flukonazole is an antifungal medication that is given either by mouth or intravenously It is used to treat a variety of fungal infections especially Candida infections of the vagina mouth throat and bloodstream It is on the World Health Organizations Mokgatlo wa Maphelo wa Lefase List of Essential Medicines a list of the most important medication needed in a basic health system Simondiu

ns Town Simons Town Afrikaans Simonstad ke toropo hleng le Cape Town Afrika Borwa ke base ya South African Navy It is located on the shores of False Bay on the eastern side of the Cape Peninsula For more than two centuries it has been an important naval base and harbour first for the Royal Navy and now the South African Navy The town is named after Simon van der Stel an early governor of the Cape Colony Wupperthal Wupperthal ke toropo wa Mmušôgaê wa Cederberg Mmasepala Setereke tša West Coast go
